{"tid":947424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥係叱咤頒獎","createTime":"2018-12-19T09:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T11:32:57.000Z","uid":117622,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb6c48f043a659d738934d790a8fc0fec23a0a5","tid":947424,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:06:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6tXHI75cQMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6tXHI75cQMA&d=4GjDEg7Vel6eijA17OryLJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d619567b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6tXHI75cQMA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e50060d9bb13325baafac9d4caf708d67aa2a3","tid":947424,"uid":197563,"like":8,"dislike":18,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"1. 出賣 back up佬<br />\n<br />\n自己老番完人再屌人老番佢 好撚無恥<br />\n<br />\n早期你未紅 back up 佬冇錢收幫你宣傳又唔撚見你出聲<br />\n<br />\n利用完人就過橋抽板 唔該都冇聲<br />\n<br />\n2. 用老番window<br />\n<br />\n比兄弟踢爆用老番window<br />\n現場live果陣仲死撐扮傻仔話&lsquo;點解會咁？&lsquo;<br />\n之後見勢色唔對同兜唔到就扮晒死狗發文道歉<br />\n<br />\n3. 偷人潮文讀<br />\n<br />\n之前有個潮文作者話過有問題<br />\n達哥未得作者批准就用人地作品做商業用途<br />\n<br />\n4. 打機唔係為錢<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母打撚到搬去康城<br />\n收錢打埋d垃圾game <br />\n又話打機唔係為錢 自打嘴巴<br />\n<br />\n5. 奶共 ，親中，黃絲變藍絲<br />\n<br />\n入左中國公司之後<br />\n逢親大是大非都唔敢出聲<br />\n（黃之峰坐監，立法會投票）<br />\n<br />\n收淘寶錢雙十一買廣告就識！<br />\n<br />\n6. 成日用蝗語 同 人口filter<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔洗講啦 向班小學雞洗腦<br />\n&emsp;"},{"pid":"76eecb02ffbd8526882a3ce152c079724f42f73f","tid":947424,"uid":197563,"like":8,"dislike":20,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:10:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 導人向善? </div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">忘恩負義 過河拆橋 人血饅頭</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;當backup佬係1，<span style=\"color: red;\">我係9</span>，但宜家係這些影